# 3. NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_* - Required for Sanity CMS connection
#
# FEATURES ENABLED BY THESE VARIABLES:
# ✅ Registration data storage in Sanity CMS
# ✅ PDF receipt generation and email delivery
# ✅ PDF receipt storage and download from admin interface
# ✅ Enhanced registration table with filtering and export
# ✅ PayPal/Razorpay payment processing
# ✅ Professional email templates with dynamic branding
